## AGENTS.md Pattern

### Root AGENTS.md

Located at project root - loaded for every AI interaction:

```markdown
# Project - AI Agent Instructions

## Quick Start
[Essential commands]

## Tech Stack
[Key technologies]

## Architecture
[High-level patterns]

## Need Help?
[Links to detailed docs]
```

### Feature AGENTS.md

Located in feature directories:

```markdown
# Feature: [Name]

## Key Files
[Important locations]

## Patterns
[Feature-specific conventions]

## Dependencies
[Related features/services]
```

