## Update Triggers

| Event | Update |
|-------|--------|
| New pattern established | Add to rules |
| Architecture change | Update AGENTS.md |
| Feature completed | Update feature docs |
| Task finished | Update TASKS.md |
| Breaking change | Add to changelog |

